  Description: 'Wound: Left arm severed at the shoulder, blood pouring freely.


    Story:
    Antonio, a Genoese sailor, wails not for himself but for his little sister back
    home. Their parents died of plague, and he was all she had left. He sobs that
    she will have no protector now, only hunger and the pity of neighbors who will
    forget her as easily as they forget him.



